  <h5 id="interviews">Interviews: Getting a list</h5>
  <p class="summary">This method returns a basic list of all the interviews.</p>
  <p>
    Requesting (GET):<br>
    <code><a href="/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/interviews" title="Request a list of all the interviews as JSON.">/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/interviews</a></code>
  </p>
  <p>Will give you:</p>
  <pre>
{
  "interviews": [
    {
      "slug": "fizban.the.fabulous",
      "name": "Fizban the Fabulous",
      "url": "http://usesthis.com/interviews/fizban.the.fabulous/",
      "summary": "Wizard",
      "date": 1425970800,
      "categories": [
        "mac",
        "wizard"
      ]
    },
    {
      "slug": "tasslehoff.burrfoot",
      "name": "Tasslehoff Burrfoot",
      "url": "http://usesthis.com/interviews/tasslehoff.burrfoot/",
      "summary": "Borrower",
      "date": 1425542400,
      "categories": [
        "linux",
        "thief"
      ]
    }
  ]
}</pre>

  <h5 id="interview">Interviews: Getting an interview</h5>
  <p class="summary">This method returns a complete interview for the given slug, including gear.</p>
  <p>
    Requesting (GET):<br>
    <code><a href="/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/interviews/<%= @site.latest_post.slug %>" title="Request a given interview as JSON.">/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/interviews/<strong><em>slug</em></strong></a></code>
  </p>
  <p>Will give you:</p>
  <pre>
{
  "interview": {
    "slug": "tasslehoff.burrfoot",
    "name": "Tasslehoff Burrfoot",
    "url": "http://usesthis.com/interviews/tasslehoff.burrfoot/",
    "summary": "Borrower",
    "date": 1425542400,
    "categories": [
      "linux",
      "thief"
    ],
    "contents": "#### Who are you, and what do you do?...",
    "gear": {
      "hardware": [
        {
          "slug": "hoopak",
          "name": "Hoopak",
          "description": "A wooden staff with a sling.",
          "url": "http://www.hoopaks-r-us.com/"
        }
      ],
      "software": [
        {
          "slug": "wanderlust",
          "name": "Wanderlust",
          "description": "A need for travel.",
          "url": "http://my-kender.net/"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}</pre>

  <h5 id="interview-categories">Interviews: Getting categories</h5>
  <p class="summary">This method returns a basic list of all the interview categories.</p>
  <p>
    Requesting (GET):<br>
    <code><a href="/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/interviews/categories" title="Request a list of all the interview categories as JSON.">/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/interviews/categories</a></code>
  </p>
  <p>Will give you:</p>
