  <h5 id="hardware">Hardware: Getting a list</h5>
  <p class="summary">This method returns a basic list of all the hardware mentioned on the site.</p>
  <p>
    Requesting (GET):<br>
    <code><a href="/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/hardware" title="Request a list of all the hardware as JSON.">/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/hardware</a></code>
