  <h5 id="hardware-item">Hardware: Getting an item</h5>
  <p class="summary">This method returns a piece of hardware for the given slug, including related interviews.</p>
  <p>
    Requesting (GET):<br>
    <code><a href="/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/hardware/macbook-pro" title="Request a given piece of hardware as JSON.">/api/v<%= UsesThis::API::VERSION %>/hardware/<strong><em>slug</em></strong></a></code>
  </p>
  <p>Will give you:</p>
  <pre>
{
  "gear": {
    "slug": "hoopak",
    "name": "Hoopak",
    "description": "A wooden staff with a sling.",
    "url": "http://www.hoopaks-r-us.com/",
    "interviews": [
      {
        "slug": "tasslehoff.burrfoot",
        "name": "Tasslehoff Burrfoot",
      }
    ]
  }
}</pre>

